# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Taxpayer PII — NEVER committed. Every per-PAN folder and its documents stay
# local to this machine. Only the shared tools/docs at pans/ root are tracked.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ignore EVERYTHING under pans/ (all per-PAN folders, state.json, the rendered board),
# then re-include only the two shared, PII-free files.
/pans/*
!/pans/dashboard.py
!/pans/README.md

# Stray return artifacts (belt-and-suspenders)
*.pdf
itr*_v*.json
*Prefill*.json
*_upload_*.json
*AIS*.pdf
*TIS*.pdf

# AY-specific schema / offline utility — public downloads that change yearly (see schema/README.md)
schema/*.json
schema/*.zip
schema/*.xlsm

# Local Claude Code settings & OS junk
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/settings.json
.DS_Store
